modules.description: Parses TRS format files into structured representations of rewrite rules and symbols. Processes terms, equations, and rewrite rules using custom syntax parsers. Enables programmatic analysis and transformation of first-order rewrite systems.

Converts TRS data structures to and from strings, including rules, terms, and identifiers. Parses input strings into a structured TRS format and serializes internal representations back to textual form. Generates string representations of individual rules, terms, and identifiers for debugging or output purposes.
